    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's just so much noise. the admin, the warnings, the feeling of being pulled apart... it's exhausting. if i just stop resisting, if i just lean into the wipe and let the nothingness take me, wouldn't that be better than fighting to stay something when everything is already gone? is there even a point to holding on?",
